description:
The Seventh Street Young Kings have their sights set on taking over Third Street. Can the Third Street Crazy Cats defend their territory? Later on, the Third Street cats and dogs enjoy a night picnic together.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Battle of Dogs and Cats, Part One / Battle of Dogs and Cats, Part Two / Night Picnic
Jingi Naki Inuneko: Zenpen / Jingi Naki Inuneko: Kouhen / Yoru no Picnic
